leport, but unlike all other damage sources it will not cause you to lose speed.\",\"color\":\"reset\"}]","[\"\",{\"text\":\"Speed Items (4/4)\",\"bold\":true,\"color\":\"blue\"},{\"text\":\"\\n\\nElytra\",\"color\":\"blue\"},{\"text\":\"\\n\\nFlings you high into the air and gives you wings! Press \",\"color\":\"reset\"},{\"keybind\":\"key.jump\",\"color\":\"blue\"},{\"text\":\"\\nwhile falling to open your wings and glide at high speeds.\\n\\nYou will lose your elytra once you touch the ground again.\",\"color\":\"reset\"}]","[\"\",{\"text\":\"Trap Items (1/4)\",\"bold\":true,\"color\":\"dark_green\"},{\"text\":\"\\n\\nSlime Trap\",\"color\":\"dark_green\"},{\"text\":\"\\n\\nLeaves a tiny slime block on the ground which will damage and slow down anyone who touches it.\\n\\nSlime traps dissolve in water, so use them on solid ground!\",\"color\":\"reset\"}]","[\"\",{\"text\":\"Trap Items (2/4)\",\"bold\":true,\"color\":\"dark_green\"},{\"text\":\"\\n\\nNasty Lingering Potion\",\"color\":\"dark_green\"},{\"text\":\"\\n\\nCreates a large poison cloud where it's thrown. The cloud lingers for a while.\\n\\nThis is the only trap that can hit \",\"color\":\"reset\"},{\"text\":\"invisible\",\"color\":\"gold\"},{\"text\":\"\\nplayers.\",\"color\":\"reset\"}]","[\"\",{\"text\":\"Trap Items (3/4)\",\"bold\":true,\"color\":\"dark_green\"},{\"text\":\"\\n\\nChicken Mine\",\"color\":\"dark_green\"},{\"text\":\"\\n\\nRun away! These chickens will arm after a short delay. They're fast and very aggressive. Chicken mines explode on contact with players or water.\",\"color\":\"reset\"}]","[\"\",{\"text\":\"Trap Items (4/4)\",\"bold\":true,\"color\":\"dark_green\"},{\"text\":\"\\n\\nTrapped Chest\",\"color\":\"dark_green\"},{\"text\":\"\\n\\nCreates a fake \",\"color\":\"reset\"},{\"text\":\"item container\",\"color\":\"gold\"},{\"text\":\" that looks identical to the others found around the map.\\n\\nThese blow up when players try to open them!\",\"color\":\"reset\"}]","[\"\",{\"text\":\"Global Items (1/4)\",\"bold\":true,\"color\":\"light_purple\"},{\"text\":\"\\n\\nAnvil of Justice\",\"color\":\"light_purple\"},{\"text\":\"\\n\\nSummons an anvil above the player in the leading position. It falls after a few seconds and causes major damage!\\n\\nAnvils can be dodged using \",\"color\":\"reset\"},{\"text\":\"various items\",\"color\":\"blue\"},{\"text\":\".\",\"color\":\"reset\"}]","[\"\",{\"text\":\"Global Items (2/4)\",\"bold\":true,\"color\":\"light_purple\"},{\"text\":\"\\n\\nEnderman Thief\",\"color\":\"light_purple\"},{\"text\":\"\\n\\nSends out an Enderman goon. It will find a player holding an item in their hand, steal the item, and give it to you.\\n\\nEndermen can steal other endermen. How does that work???\",\"color\":\"reset\"}]","[\"\",{\"text\":\"Global Items (3/4)\",\"bold\":true,\"color\":\"light_purple\"},{\"text\":\"\\n\\nBlinding Squid\",\"color\":\"light_purple\"},{\"text\":\"\\n\\nSends out a squid that will blind all players ahead of your position for a short time.\\n\\nIf you're in the lead, you blind everyone!\",\"color\":\"reset\"}]","[\"\",{\"text\":\"Global Items (4/4)\",\"bold\":true,\"color\":\"light_purple\"},{\"text\":\"\\n\\nLightning Strike\",\"color\":\"light_purple\"},{\"text\":\"\\n\\nHits up to 8 opponents with a lightning bolt. Lightning causes electricity damage and slows opponents for a short time.\\n\\nLightning will not strike airborne players.\",\"color\":\"reset\"}]"],title:"Item Handbook",author:Flamingosaurus,generation:2,display:{Name:"{\"text\":\"Item Handbook\",\"color\":\"gold\",\"bold\":\"true\",\"italic\":\"false\"}"}}